About
-----

  Airopdate is a simple shell script that allows you to get various versions of
  aircrack-ng, airoscript and drivers for multiple wifi devices.

Sections
---------

  1 - aircrack-ng : allows you to get any version of 
      aircrack-ng : stable, latest svn, latest 1.0-dev,
      or a specific revision

  2 - drivers	: allows you to install drivers automatically.
      For now only a few drivers are supported. 
      (DEPRECATED, use airdriver-ng instad)

  3 - airoscript : allows you to get the latest version 
